welcome_message_body: Welcome to Alafaya, where charming neighborhoods, beautiful parks, and a vibrant community await you. Known for its friendly locals and diverse culinary scene, we invite you to explore and enjoy all that our city has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orlando Executive Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Orlando Executive Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orlando International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: Terminal A handles domestic flights for airlines such as American Airlines, JetBlue, and Southwest.

terminals.name: Terminal B
terminals.description: Terminal B serves international flights for airlines such as Air Canada, British Airways, and Lufthansa.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free wifi network for up to 4 hours.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kissimmee Gateway Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Kissimmee Gateway Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orlando Sanford International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Orlando Sanford International Airport primarily serves international flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free WiFi throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Space Coast Regional Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Space Coast Regional Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free wifi throughout the airport.
